            <title>[OPENJPA-823] Add JPA 2.0 schemas and appropriately validate for version</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/OPENJPA-823</link>
                <project id="12310351" key="OPENJPA">OpenJPA</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This task is to update OpenJPA to:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;a) Include the new JPA 2.0 xsd&apos;s.&lt;br/&gt;
b) Validate using the appropriate xsd based on the version specified in the persistence.xml or orm.xml.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
